{"tid":889058,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解以前啲中文係右至左咁睇？","createTime":"2018-11-04T09:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T18:12:46.000Z","uid":113837,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d8f9e84e2b2b3b17aab446151234db20555be5","tid":889058,"uid":113837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"我睇睇好辛苦，完全睇唔到，個腦就爆咁"},{"pid":"6f7ad2e16e9fb15b326f6149562c8cb3c912b85b","tid":889058,"uid":113837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"？睇咁左至右係文中啲前以解點"},{"pid":"354dc0d636d8d76618a0686ac1a2d066c26db31d","tid":889058,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:37:46.000Z","msg":"上至下 , 右至左<br />\n<img src=\"http://i3.sinaimg.cn/history/2015/0527/U11616P1488DT20150527114939.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.sinaimg.cn%2Fhistory%2F2015%2F0527%2FU11616P1488DT20150527114939.jpg&h=7ab01bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於這個由右至左直書文字的習慣，則是源自於古時候人們使用竹簡（狹長形的竹片）書寫文字之故，當時大部分慣用右手寫字的人在竹簡上寫字時，為了方便左手順勢補上空白竹簡，以利下一片竹簡的書寫；於是竹簡「由右至左」的排列方式，便決定了文字的閱讀方向，亦成了後來在紙張上書寫文字的統一方向（由右至左直書）。"},{"pid":"4641eccdbb301c6ee1405254d5c6e1bd302976a2","tid":889058,"uid":17502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f7ad2e16e9fb15b326f6149562c8cb3c912b85b","tid":889058,"uid":113837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"？睇咁左至右係文中啲前以解點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:38:38.000Z","msg":"唔會好似你咁憨鳩淨係得右至左"},{"pid":"e233368863c66739bff7d41fe1de446addeaa8f8","tid":889058,"uid":82078,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:40:04.000Z","msg":"因為右至左咁寫囉<br />\n點解咁寫係因為以前個袖口大又長 右手寫字由左至右就hi到個袖都係墨<br />\n就算用左手拿高右邊個袖都會整污糟左邊袖<br />\n但係由右至左就冇呢個問題"},{"pid":"87c06d1fde2a97ef6f23fec2529e4e75b74c7526","tid":889058,"uid":82078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e233368863c66739bff7d41fe1de446addeaa8f8","tid":889058,"uid":82078,"like":0,"dislike"